  <brief_title>Comparison of Two Types of Braces in the Treatment of Rockwood Type III AC-dislocations</brief_title>
  <official_title>Conservative Treatment of Rockwood Type III Acromioclavicular Dislocation With Two Different Types of Braces: a Comparative Prospective Randomized Trial</official_title>
